Class CSCollaborativeSpaceSelector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jalios.jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.CSCollaborativeSpaceSelector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.jalios.jcms.DataSelector, java.util.function.Predicate<com.jalios.jcms.Data>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CSManager.MemberCollaborativeSpaceSelector, CSManager.MemberOtherCollaborativeSpaceSelector, CSTypologySelector
    public class CSCollaborativeSpaceSelector
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.jalios.jcms.DataSelector
    Allows to filter on only not model, not closed, and readable CollaborativeSpaces.

    By default, does not return model or closed spaces.

    Since:
    csp-7.3
    Author:
